Check the branch code of Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Corporation Bank by using IFSC Code

As per our database, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Corporation Bank ifsc code is CORP0000136, the first 4 digits of the IFSC represent Corporation Bank and last 6 characters (i.e. 000901) represent the Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch and the 5th character is zero. So, 000901 is the branch code of Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Corporation Bank.

Corporation Bank, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Branch FAQ

What is the ifsc code for Corporation Bank Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch?

The IFSC Code of Corporation Bank Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch is CORP0000136 and same code you can also find on cheque and bank passbook of Corporation Bank bank Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch. The ifsc code: CORP0000136 is used for RTGS, NEFT and IMPS transactions.

What are the bank times for Corporation Bank, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch?

The Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch of Corporation Bank, will work from Mondays to Saturdays and the timings are from 10 AM to 4 PM IST (tentatively) but 2nd and 4th Saturdays will be bank holiday.

What is the address of Corporation Bank, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch?

The address of the Corporation Bank Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Branch is Sri Ranga Comm Complex Badi Chowdi Hyderabad 500195, Hyderabad, Telangana.

What is the branch code of Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Corporation Bank?

000136 is the branch code of Hyderabad Badi Chowdi Corporation Bank.

Where to check Corporation Bank, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch holidays?

Bank holidays are differ from state to state across India, so to know the details of bank holidays for each state, just go visit bank site and can click on the bank holidays.

What is the format of IFSC Code of Corporation Bank Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch?

IFSC-CORP0000136 is the 11-character code with the first four alphabetic characters indicates the bank name, and the last six characters (either numerical or alphabetical) specifies the branch. The fifth character is 0 (zero) and it reserved for future use. Check below the format of CORP0000136.

CORP : bank code

0 : Reserved for future use

000136 : branch code

How can I contact Corporation Bank, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch?

If you are a customer of Corporation Bank, Hyderabad Badi Chowdi branch then you can physically visit the branch on working days. The bank is also providing customer support through phone and email so, you may also call or mail on below phone number or email id to clarify your query. Better visit branch unless it is not urgent.
